            "width": 464,
            "height": 512,
            "content": "# 🟪 Artifact Handling\n\n- Extract generated image/video IDs from VLM Run response.\n  - Plain: img_182573\n  - With tags: img_c7ae8c\n- Fetch artifacts using:\n  - Get Image Artifact → img_* ID\n- Artifacts are ready to send or further \nprocess in the workflow."
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
